## Introduction
Once again I was part of the Android254 Jetpack Compose Study Jam panel. 
This was a part of a multi-series study jam in association with Women Techmakers Nairobi.

Alongside fellow panelists Evans Chepsiror and Harun Wangereka and moderated by Mambo Brian and Annie Kobia,
we had a question and answers exchange with learners participating in the program.

## Presentation
This panel discussion is not recorded. 
It was done to a live audience at iHub, Nairobi Kenya.
